angkok Dangerous]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[Bangkok Dangerous (1999 film)|Bangkok Dangerous]]'' (1999)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Shutter (2008 film)|Shutter]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[Shutter (2004 film)|Shutter]]'' (2004)\n| \n|}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:English-language films with previous foreign-language film versions}}\n[[Category:Lists of remake films]]\n[[Category:English-language films|Foreign-language films]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\n{{inc-film}}\nThis list includes both English-language films that were based on previously released foreign-language films and those that were not based on any previous film, but merely share a common source material.\n\n== Chinese ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Chinese-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[The Departed]]'' (2006)\n| ''[[Infernal Affairs]]'' (2002) (Cantonese)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Eye (2008 film)|The Eye]]'' (2008)\n| ''[[The Eye (2002 film)|The Eye]]'' (2002) (Various languages: Cantonese / Mandarin)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Tortilla Soup]]'' (2001)\n| ''[[Eat Drink Man Woman]]'' (1994) (Mandarin)\n| \n|}\n\n== Czech ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Czech-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Pickup (1951 film)|Pickup]]'' (1951)\n| ''Hl\u00edda\u010d \u010d. 47'' (1937)\n| The novel ''Guard No. 47'' ([[Josef Kopta]])\n|}\n\n== Danish ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! English-language film\n! Danish-language film\n! Common source material (if any)\n|-\n| ''[[Brothers (2009 film)|Brothers]]'' (2009)\n| ''[[Brothers (2004 film)|Br\u00f8dre]]'' (2004)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Catch That Kid]]'' (2004)\n| ''[[Klatret\u00f8sen]]'' (2002)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The First Time (2009 film)|The First Time]]'' (2009)\n| ''[[Love at First Hiccough|K\u00e6rlighed ved f\u00f8rste hik]]'' (1999)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Nightwatch (1997 film)|Nightwatch]]'' (1997)\n| ''[[Nightwatch (1994 film)|Nattevagten]]'' (1994)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Pusher (2012 film)|Pusher]]'' (2012)