e Silent Battle]]'' (1939)\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|La Bataille silencieuse|fr}}'' (1937)\n| The novel ''Le Poisson chinois'' (Jean Bommart)\n|-\n| ''[[Sleepless (2017 film)|Sleepless]]'' (2017)\n| ''[[Sleepless Night (2011 film)|Nuit Blanche]]'' (2011)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Soldier and the Lady]]'' (1937)\n| ''[[Michel Strogoff (1936 film)|Michel Strogoff]]'' (1936)\n| The novel ''[[Michael Strogoff]]'' ([[Jules Verne]])\n|-\n| ''[[Some Like It Hot]]'' (1959)\n| ''[[Fanfare d'amour]]'' (1935)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Sommersby]]'' (1993)\n| ''[[Le Retour De Martin Guerre]]'' (1982)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Sorcerer (film)|Sorcerer]]'' (1977)\n| ''[[The Wages of Fear|Le Salaire de la Peur]]'' (1953)\n| The novel ''Le Salaire de la peur'' ([[Georges Arnaud]])\n|-\n| ''[[Special Correspondents]]'' (2016)\n| ''[[Envoy\u00e9s tr\u00e8s sp\u00e9ciaux]]'' (2009)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Station Six-Sahara]]'' (1962)\n| ''[[S.O.S. Sahara]]'' (1938, Germany)\n| The play ''Men Without a Past'' (Jean Martet)\n|-\n| ''[[Stranger in the House (1967 film)|Stranger in the House]]'' (1967)\n| ''[[The Strangers in the House (film)|Les Inconnus dans la maison]]'' (1942)\n| The novel ''[[The Strangers in the House]]'' ([[Georges Simenon]])\n|-\n| ''[[Sweet Devil]]'' (1938)\n| ''[[Quelle dr\u00f4le de gosse!]]'' (1935)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Talented Mr. Ripley (film)|The Talented Mr. Ripley]]'' (1999)\n| ''[[Purple Noon|Plein soleil]]'' (1960)\n| The novel ''[[The Talented Mr. Ripley]]'' ([[Patricia Highsmith]])\n|-\n| ''[[Taxi (2004 film)|Taxi]]'' (2004)\n| ''[[Taxi (1998 film)|Taxi]]'' (1998)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Temptation Harbour]]'' (1947)\n| ''L'Homme de Londres'' (1943)\n| The novel ''Newhaven-Dieppe (L'Homme de Londres)'' ([[Georges Simenon]])\n|-\n| ''[[Three Fugitives]]'' (1989)\n| ''[[Les Fugitifs]]'' (1986)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Three Maxims]]'' (1936)\n| ''{{ill|Vari\u00e9t\u00e9s (film)|fr|3=Vari\u00e9t\u00e9s (film, 1935)|lt=Vari\u00e9t\u00e9s}}'' (1935)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Three Men and a Baby]]'' (1987)\n| ''[[Three Men and a Cradle|Trois hommes et un couffin]]'' (1985)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Tourist (2010 film)|The Tourist]]'' (2010)\n| ''[[Anthony Zimmer]]'' (2005)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Tovarich (film)|Tovarich]]'' (1937)\n| ''[[Tovaritch (film)|Tovaritch]]'' (1935)\n| The play ''Tovaritch'' ([[Jacques Deval]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Toy (1982 film)|The Toy]]'' (1982)\n| ''[[Le Jouet]]'' (1976)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Trap for Cinderella (2013 film)|Trap for Cinderella]]'' (2013)\n| ''[[Trap for Cinderella (1965 film)|Pi\u00e8ge pour Cendrillon]]'' (1965)\n| The novel ''[[Pi\u00e8ge pour Cendrillon]]'' ([[S\u00e9bastien Japrisot]])\n|-\n| ''[[True Lies]]'' (1994)\n| ''[[La Totale!]]'' (1991)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Tunnel (1935 film)|The Tunnel]]'' (1935)\n| ''[[Le tunnel]]'' (1933)\n| The novel ''[[Der Tunnel (novel)|Der Tunnel]]'' ([[Bernhard Kellermann]])\n|-\n| ''[[12 Monkeys (film)|Twelve Monkeys]]'' (1995)\n| ''[[La Jet\u00e9e]]'' (1962)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Two Men in Town (2014 film)|Two Men in Town]]'' (2014)\n| ''[[Two Men in Town (1973 film)|Deux hommes dans la ville]]'' (1973)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Two Much]]'' (1995)\n| ''[[The Twin (1984 film)|Le Jumeau]]'' (1984)\n| The novel ''Two Much'' ([[Donald E. Westlake]])\n|-\n| ''[[Under Suspicion (2000 film)|Under Suspicion]]'' (2000)\n| ''[[Garde \u00e0 Vue]]'' (1981)\n| The novel ''Brainwash'' ([[John Wainwright (author)|John Wainwright]])\n|-\n| ''[[Unfaithful (2002 film)|Unfaithful]]'' (2002)\n| ''[[The Unfaithful Wife|La Femme infid\u00e8le]]'' (1968)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Unfinished Dance]]'' (1947)\n| ''[[La mort du cygne]]'' (1937)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Upside]]'' (2017)\n| ''[[The Intouchables]]'' (2011)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Violent Road]]'' (1958)\n| ''[[The Wages of Fear|Le Salaire de la Peur]]'' (1953)\n| The novel ''Le Salaire de la peur'' ([[Georges Arnaud]])\n|-\n| ''[[War of the Buttons (1994 film)|War of the Buttons]]'' (1994)\n| ''[[La Guerre des boutons (film, 1962)|La Guerre des boutons]]'' (1962)\n| The novel ''[[La Guerre des boutons (novel)|La Guerre